      "title": "Water tariffs to go up from Sept. 1",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A gazette to be issued notifying the increase to water tariffs with effect from September 1, the National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NWSDB) said.",
        "Sources close to the Board said the special gazette notification will be issued later today, to notify the increase of the service charge to Rs.300.\u00a0 (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
